{"tid":2194310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科大經濟學系教授：介定接受檢測者為「好市民」應規定只有接受檢測的市民，可受惠於政府的派錢或紓困措施","createTime":"2020-09-08T12:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T14:19:18.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42661f215cb6670a7ab4c994ccce10c0b84141ef","tid":2194310,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"【有團體建議強制全民檢測　倡檢測與派錢掛勾】<br />\n<br />\n團體「民眾聯席」呼籲市民參與普及社區檢測，同時建議政府強制全民檢測，並持續為市民進行抽樣測試，以盡快重啟本港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n科大經濟學系榮休教授雷鼎鳴建議，全民檢測可與跨境健康碼掛勾，亦可以介定接受檢測者為「好市民」，日後可優先接種疫苗，亦應規定只有接受檢測的市民，可受惠於政府的派錢或紓困措施。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #RTHK #民眾聯席 #雷鼎鳴 #全民檢測<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3815079005266794/?vh=e&amp;extid=dn5MxRD0XcktS5Zn&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3815079005266794%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3Ddn5MxRD0XcktS5Zn%26d%3Dn&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d0d08db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3815079005266794/?vh=e&amp;extid=dn5MxRD0XcktS5Zn&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b205247d7bb8ab7a777789f46800fee070fd2f0e","tid":2194310,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"雷鼎鳴，BBS，JP（Francis T. Lui），中華人民共和國廣東台山人，香港科技大學經濟學系前系主任及榮休教授，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>香港建制派政治組織幫港出聲成員</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83455d22eb6858d8697d6f05b54f4e6f33d5203b","tid":2194310,"uid":231583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7f2353d17e8baee28298a2add1ab4c4b9023f30","tid":2194310,"uid":346260,"like":0,"disli